Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing but the\Nson of a filthy pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filthy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must truly hate your\Ngreat idiot of a father
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for abandoning his family and village\Nbecause of his lust for treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare insult\Nmy father any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:03:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only then will I inherit\Nher enormous fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys! Don't attack that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Expose the Plot!\NPirate Butler Captain Kuro"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain's been gone a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a big shock for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always watches the sea from\Nthe shore when he's feeling down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain!\N--Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wasn't Luffy with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain!\N--Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Luffy?\NWasn't he at the shore with...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he still mad about\Nhis dad being insulted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that look was different!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something must've happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you suppose he\Nlooked so desperate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how do we get\Nto this shore of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this smell like an incident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something must've\Nhappened at the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this calls for the Usopp Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, already!\NHow do we get there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Terrible... news...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrible news, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are going to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning, pirates are\Ngoing to attack this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, run away! Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all doing?! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Usopp! Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:06:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna pay once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! All you ever\Ndo is spout huge lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were as honest as Klahadore-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then we'd believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what he does,\Nit won't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning, Jango.\NAttack the village at daybreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he ignored me because\Nnobody'd believe me anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones you custom-ordered\Nfrom the eyewear shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the next town over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they're perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for asking you\Nto go all the way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a present, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Tomorrow is actually\Nexactly three years since the day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klahadore came to this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always taken good care of me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klahadore-san will be delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, hear me out, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates really are going to\Nattack tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we believed every\Nstory you ever told,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd have fled the village\Nhundreds of times by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, believe me!\NWe gotta get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They really are going to kill everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear it's the truth this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're gonna get you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him! Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain always heals\Nhis emotional pain here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is nice here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That straw hat guy isn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty fragile here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami. Don't fall now.\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Look! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the--?!\N--There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's the straw hat guy!\N--And his butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! How did this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He fell!\N--He's a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why our captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might never come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta run, Kaya!\NThey're gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:10:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been tricked!\NThat butler is really a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. What kind of joke is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no joke!\NI heard it with my own ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klahadore's really a pirate who\Nweaseled his way into your mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he could get your fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been pretending to be a\Nbutler for three years straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he could get your fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Usopp-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said his crew's gonna storm\Nin and kill you at dawn tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a really bad guy!\NYou gotta escape, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I admit, he did say too much earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But lying like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you, Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! They're going to kill Kaya-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really going\Nto attack the village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what they said.\NNo question about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what were you\Nsleeping down here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was up on the cliff...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So how'd I get down here?\N--I knew it! Klahadore's a bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder he seemed so creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why our captain ran to\Nthe village with that intense look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now they'll know, and\Ncan run away beforehand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about stupid bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!\NWe gotta run away, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We gotta organize\Nall our prized possessions...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...and hurry!\N--...and hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, no!\N--What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to stock up on food\Nbefore the meat shop guy runs away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue at hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Usopp-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of story do you have today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Hmm, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This story happened when I was five,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I fought a giant goldfish\Nliving in the southern sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goldfish? You fought a goldfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It was so big,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not even a fish tank the size\Nof this mansion could've held it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What first shocked me was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the immense size\Nand length of its poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so big that I landed on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking it was solid ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it does, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, first off, starting a bonfire to\Ndry off my clothes was a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How come?\N--Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the goldfish's butt caught\Non fire and freaked it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I guess I can't say I blame it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so close to\Nbecoming a grilled goldfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I loved them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved the lies you told...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, why are you saying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that! I'm not\Ntrying to get back at Klahadore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter, Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta escape, Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta get out of this village,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before that butler gets back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll all make sense come tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you gotta escape for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He roughed up the lady of the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How horrible!\N--How could he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...won't anyone believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pull yourself together, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's truly been three long years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once this plan succeeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to give you\Nall plenty of the take.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At dawn tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,destroy the village\Nto your hearts' content!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Usopp!\NA brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you've been unhappy lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cheer you up with a story!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave! I'll call for someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:18:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, don't sweat it!\NI'm always meddlesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was three, my meddling\Neven led me to save a sick whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh? A whale?\N--You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was huge, and had\Na really sore throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I went inside its mouth,\Nbut it thought I was food!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning, Jango.\NAttack the village at daybreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain!\N--Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alive? Yeah, I just woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy was asleep the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, Captain!\NWe heard everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and tell\Neveryone about the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! All you ever\Ndo is spout huge lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were as honest as Klahadore-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then we'd believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lying like usual, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn butler pissed me off,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided to claim he's a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you put the straw\Nhat guy up to it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think less of you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Me too.\N--Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that butler is a jerk,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd\Nlie to hurt someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really respected you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was all wrong about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Same here!\N--Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's suppertime!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder what we're having...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, all done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you tell them that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were never going to\Nbelieve me from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was too optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, the truth is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates really are going\Nto come, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They're definitely gonna show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone thinks it's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They think tomorrow'll be just\Nanother normal, peaceful day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to stop the\Npirates at the beach tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make sure this stays a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only logical thing\Nfor a liar like me to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I get shot in the arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if I'm driven off with brooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is my village!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.89,0:21:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one hell of a nice guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushing your henchmen away\Nand going into battle alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I have dibs\Non all the pirates' treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.67,0:21:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We'll help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys... are going\Nto fight with me?! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a whole bunch\Nof bad guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Scared" is written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me, scared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly okay with lots\Nof bad guys or whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm Captain Usopp,\Nbrave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Dammit! This isn't a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Klahadore's\Npirates we're dealing with!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.76,0:22:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm scared!\NWhat's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your sympathy!\NYou guys can leave! Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't laughing! We're helping\N'cause we think you're honorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if we'd risk our lives\Nbecause of sympathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.52,0:22:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:23:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:24:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.14,0:24:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why'd Usopp\Ncover this slope in oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.31,0:24:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's his Oil Strategy.\N--What a weird strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.61,0:24:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where are the pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.41,0:24:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They're at the north shore?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.85,0:24:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll go on ahead!\N--They're gonna take my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.19,0:24:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,North, north! Which way is north?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.72,0:24:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.42,0:24:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Clash with the Black Cat Pirates!\NGreat Battle on the Slope!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.06,0:24:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
